OL,3,CVoters choose their MP for the second
OL,4,Ctime in six months
OL,6,FITV Granada's Political Correspondent
OL,7,FElaine Willcox talks to the candidates
OL,9,FVoters in Rochdale are preparing to
OL,10,Fvote for their MP for the second time
OL,11,Fin six months.
OL,13,FA by-election was called in February
OL,14,Fafter the death of veteran Labour MP
OL,15,FSir Tony Lloyd, who had held the seat
OL,16,Fsince 2010.
