OL,3,CVoters choose their MP for the second
OL,4,Ctime in six months
OL,6,FVoters were left with an unusual
OL,7,Fchoice after Labour withdrew its
OL,8,Fsupport for their official candidate
OL,9,FAzhar Ali following comments he made
OL,10,Fabout the 7 October attacks on Israel,
OL,11,Fbut he remained on the ballot paper as
OL,12,Fthe deadline had passed.
OL,14,FThe by-election was won by leader of
OL,15,Fthe Workers Party of Britain, George
OL,16,FGalloway on a pro-Palestine ticket.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
