OL,6,FAround a third of Rochdale's
OL,7,Fpopulation is Muslim and there was
OL,8,Ffrustration with what was seen as a
OL,9,Flack of urgency and action from Labour
OL,10,Fand the Conservatives in calling for a
OL,11,Fceasefire.
OL,13,FMr Galloway only held the seat for a
OL,14,Flittle over three months before the
OL,15,Felection was called.
OL,17,FHe said in the 54 sitting days in
OL,18,FParliament he had achieved more than
OL,19,Fthe last four MPs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
