OL,6,FHis campaign literature says Rochdale
OL,7,Fis reborn after he had secured a
OL,8,Fcommitment from the Health Minister to
OL,9,Freinstate the town's maternity
OL,10,Fservices, which were closed more than
OL,11,Fa decade ago.
OL,13,FAlthough the commitment was news to
OL,14,Fthe NHS with The Northern Care
OL,15,FAlliance, which runs the hospital,
OL,16,Fsaying it had not been involved in any
OL,17,F'high level' plans to reinstate
OL,18,Fmaternity services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
