OL,6,FGeorge Galloway said it was "absurd
OL,7,Fyou can no longer be born in
OL,8,FRochdale", unless that is you give
OL,9,Fbirth at home and he raised the issue
OL,10,Fin parliament soon after his by-
OL,11,Felection win.
OL,13,FHe said after making 'his
OL,14,Fbreakthrough' on maternity services he
OL,15,Fis now calling for the hospital's A&E
OL,16,Fto be reinstated.
OL,18,F"A town is not a town unless you can
OL,19,Fbe born in it. A town is not a town
OL,20,Funless you have an A&E," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
