OL,6,FWhen asked about his other
OL,7,Fachievements, he said he spoke more in
OL,8,Fparliament than any other MP, raising
OL,9,Fhealth and housing issues and just
OL,10,Funder half of his speeches were about
OL,11,FGaza.
OL,13,F"There is a genocide going on in Gaza
OL,14,Fyou know," he said.
OL,16,FLabour's candidate Paul Waugh, was
OL,17,Fborn and brought up in Rochdale,
OL,18,Freturning to live in his mother's
OL,19,Fcouncil house during his campaigning
OL,20,Fnext to Rochdale FC where he has a
OL,21,Fseason ticket.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
