OL,6,FHe has been a political journalist and
OL,7,Fcolumnist for 26 years, and said it
OL,8,Fwas "time to cease being a spectator
OL,9,Fand have to take part to advocate for
OL,10,Fthe town and public services".
OL,12,FHe said: "What saddens me is George
OL,13,FGalloway is pretending to bring
OL,14,Fmaternity services back to Rochdale,
OL,15,Fhe hasn't and it is fake news on his
OL,16,Fcampaign leaflets."
OL,18,FThe journalist, a father of three,
OL,19,Fsaid his wife was a midwife in the NHS
OL,20,Fand it was on it's knees and that's
OL,21,Fwhen he decided to stand for election.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
