OL,6,FWhen asked about voters frustration
OL,7,Fover Labour's delay in calling for a
OL,8,Fceasefire in Gaza, he said "we have
OL,9,Fheard the people when it comes to
OL,10,FPalestine, adding he had a long track
OL,11,Frecord on Palestinian rights".
OL,13,FIn its manifesto, Labour has committed
OL,14,Fto recognising a Palestinian state,
OL,15,Fand wants a renewed peace process
OL,16,Fwhich results in a two-state solution,
OL,17,Fwith a safe and secure Israel
OL,18,Falongside a viable and sovereign
OL,19,FPalestinian state.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
