OL,4,Ctime in six months
OL,6,FCllr Andy Kelly, is the Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat candidate, and was also born
OL,8,Fin Rochdale.
OL,10,FHe had spent his 54 years in the town
OL,11,Fand said his record on the council
OL,12,Fshows he is "active and committed to
OL,13,Fchange in the town".
OL,15,FHe said he would set up an office in
OL,16,Fthe town, open seven days a week to be
OL,17,Fvisible to constituents.
OL,19,FHe wanted to know how many of the
OL,20,Fcandidates were planning to stay in
OL,21,FRochdale after the election on 4 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
