OL,6,FHe said his party were the first to
OL,7,Fcall a motion calling for a ceasefire
OL,8,Fin Gaza, and negotiations to release
OL,9,Fhostages and create a two state
OL,10,Fsolution, although that has not
OL,11,Ftranslated into votes for the Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrats.
OL,14,F"We're an industrial town, but we
OL,15,Fdon't have the right industries
OL,16,Fanymore," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
