OL,6,F"So we have to be creative about who
OL,7,Fwe bring in, who we try and retain. If
OL,8,Fwe can introduce university courses
OL,9,Finto the town and attract and retain
OL,10,Ftalent here.
OL,12,F"But we have to also make some hard
OL,13,Fdecisions about housing. We're going
OL,14,Fto have to look after the people that
OL,15,Fare already here. Instead of just
OL,16,Fbuilding five bedroom developments in
OL,17,Fthe greenbelt."
OL,19,FThe Conservative Party candidate Paul
OL,20,FEllison was unwell at time of
OL,21,Finterview.
