OL,6,FIn a statement he said: "I am the only
OL,7,Fcandidate who not only knows the
OL,8,Fborough and its people better than
OL,9,Fany, but I have a 30 year track record
OL,10,Fof delivering my promise to make our
OL,11,Ftown a better place."
OL,13,FMichael Howard for Reform UK said he
OL,14,Fdid not engage with the media.
